Unfortunately, my page takes that mapping for granted, and only explicitly states the mapping for the letters that aren&#39;t in the Shavian alphabet. 

Here&#39;s some documentation on the mapping of the main letters at:
http://www.demeyere.com/shavian/shavian.pdf


